001package com.randomnoun.common.db.to;
002
003import org.apache.log4j.Logger;
004
005/** Holds type information for a table column. 
006 */
007public class MysqlTableColumnTO extends TableColumnTO {
008        
009        Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(MysqlTableColumnTO.class);
010
011        private String columnType;
012        
013        public MysqlTableColumnTO(TableTO table, String name, long columnId, boolean isPrimaryKey, String dataType,
014                long dataTypeLength, long dataTypePrecision, long dataScale, 
015                boolean nullable, String defaultValue, String comments) 
016        {
017                super(table, name, columnId, isPrimaryKey, dataType, dataTypeLength, dataTypePrecision, dataScale,
018                                nullable, defaultValue, comments);
019        }
020
021        public String getColumnType() {
022                return columnType;
023        }
024
025        public void setColumnType(String columnType) {
026                this.columnType = columnType;
027        }
028        
029        
030}
